  "texts": [
    "The restricted quantity of PSE reports might also result in an underestimation of the ML classifier's actual capabilities [12].",
    "Third, the quality of the LIME explanations was assessed by 2 graduate students; thus, further investigation is needed for a more robust validation of explanation quality.",
    "Furthermore, we have not yet empirically tested the interface for potential decision-making biases it may introduce.Future research should investigate the performance of ML classifiers trained with contextual text representations on a larger and more diverse data set.",
    "Additionally, while we plan to refine the interface and test whether it supports event classification, future research can continue to investigate the appropriate way of incorporating the ML classifier into the reporting and reviewing workflow of PSE report classification and examine various human-AI collaboration approaches.",
    "Future studies should explore the potential biases (ie, automation bias) that the interface may introduce into the analysts' decision-making process."
